<li>Creating graphs: <a href="http://www.gnuplot.info/"  class="extlink extlink-icon-1"  >gnuplot</a> or <a href="http://gri.sourceforge.net/"  class="extlink extlink-icon-1"  >gri graphing language</a> as an alternative</li>
